				<td colspan="2"><span>Well all I need to find out some info on EQ after being away from it for over 1 year. 
<br />

<br />
First is, whats the best class in ur opinion to duo with a cleric? ( me and my wife will be playing 2 gether all the time and she wants to be a cleri. that said I want a class that will not only be good for the low lvls but also good at high lvls and nothave to rely on any other person than my wifes cleric) 
<br />

<br />
2nd What is ur reason for choosing that class  
<br />

<br />
I think I have come up with 4 choices. 
<br />

<br />
1. Mage  Pro's: they are good solo ( till lvl 54ish) 
<br />
Con's: they are usless at raids, Epic is ubber hard to get. 
<br />

<br />
2. Necro Pro's: good snare and dot spells can mana feed a cleric, strong pet in higher lvl's 
<br />
Con's: low hp, hated 
<br />

<br />
3.Monk Pro's: good puller, can tank, cheep to gear up 
<br />
Con's: will be a mana drain 
<br />

<br />
4. Bard Pro's: can do allmost any thing 
<br />
Con's: Gets hit like a ranger lol 
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Please dont get mad at me if I missed any thing like I said I have been away from eq for a while now and forgot way to much stuff 
<br />
</span></td>
