				<td colspan="2"><span>first of all, a cleric is a pretty horrible duo with any class.  If a cleric partners with a tank.  you will have crappy DPS, and the cleric will burn too much mana healing unslowed things.  if a cleric partners with a kiting class, their nukes are pretty lame.  with a DPS class the cleric as to tank, usually unslowed things.  With a slowing class usually you are lacking in DPS and things take too long to die.
<br />

<br />
However, I strongly encourage you to play a tank class.  Warrior or shadowknight best.  Because you will be the foundation to many good groups.  just add a bard and a necro and you will find yourself plowing through mobs.  or a BST and a rogue.  or a shaman and a mage.
<br />

<br />
the only groups that don't NEED a healer and a tank are kiting groups, and like I said clerics are pretty lame in kiting groups.  And with a cleric and a war/SK you have the best healer, and the best tank(s) with decent DPS for plowing thru those levels.</span></td>
